quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa ardunoo e ma…ì…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen …ìanngu…óe, …ìe wi'i: ∆äum wonaali, si wanaa fenaande nde Muusaa fefindii. Men naniraali …óum baabiraa…ìe amen adinoo…ìe …ìen."
  28,37,"Muusaa maakani Fir'awna: Ko Joomi am …ìuri anndude on hanndude e peewal, ngal o immode ka Makko, e on mo battane mo∆¥∆¥e woodani laakara. Pellet, O malnataa too√±oo…ìe …ìen O dadndataa…ìe ko…ìe hulata ko."
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'ani dental mun ngal: Ko onon yo dental, mi anndanaa on rewetee…óo, si wanaa min. Ko an yo Haamaana, hu…ì…ìanam yiite e loopal ngal, haa wula, mahiranaa lam hu…ìeere toowunde, ndaarugol no mi ∆¥ellitora e Rewetee…óo Muusaa On; tawde mi…óo sikki mo fenoowo, e ko o nodditorta Nulaa…óo Alla e am, min e yim…ìe am."
  28,39,"Fir'awna e koneeli mun …óin hattini e mawnintinagol, townitoora e leydi Misra ndin, ko aldaa e goonga. ∆Åe yeddi ummital, …ìe sikki wonnde …ìe ruttitetaake ka Amen, √ëalnde Darngal, fii hasbeede leptee."
  28,40,"Men nanngi Fir'awna e koneeli makko …óin, Men bugii …ìe ka maayo, …ìe yoolii haa …ìe halkiii e mun. An Nulaa…óo, tesko, ko honno battane too√±u…ìe …ìen wa'unoo. Ko halkaare …ìe sakkitornoo."
  28,41,"Men wa…ói …ìe ardii…ìe bew…ìe e majju…ìe …ìen, hi…ìe nodda e Yiite ngen, saakitugol majjere e keeferaaku. √ëalnde Darngal non, …ìe walliroytaake faabo ka Yiite, wurin ko lepte …óen sowirantee…ìe, sabu ko …ìe sinciri bon…ói, …ìe noddi e majjere; …ìe winndiranaa bone huuwugol …óum, e kala jokku…óo …ìe e mun."
  28,42,"Men jokkintinira …ìe lepte …óen ka aduna …óoo, kuddi e jeesere. √ëalnde Darngal kadi, ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe e wo…ó…óintinoytee…ìe e yurmeende Alla nden."
  28,43,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere Tawreeta nden, …ìaawo nde Men nulunoo e mofte adinno…ìe …ìen, …ìe fenni Nulaa…ìe …ìen, Men halkiri …ìe sabu …óum. Nden Deftere, ko ndayginorde yim…ìe …ìen: hino e mayre ko nafata …ìe, si …ìe gollitirii; e ko lorrata …ìe, si …ìe ha…óitike e mun. Hino ton kadi ko …óowa …ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ere, e yurmeende mo∆¥∆¥ere aduna e laakara. Belajo'o, …ìe annditay neemaaji Alla …óin e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe yetta Mo, …ìe gom…óina Mo."